```json
{
  "application": "MPI",
  "details": {
    "resource_requirements": {
      "walltime": "0:10:00",
      "queue": "workq",
      "filesystems": "home:tegu",
      "account": "datascience",
      "nodes": 2
    },
    "software_requirements": {
      "modules": [
        "conda",
        "aws-ofi-nccl/v1.9.1-aws",
        "hwloc"
      ],
      "libraries": [
        "nccl",
        "lib fabric"
      ],
      "environment_variables": [
        "NCCL_NET_GDR_LEVEL=PHB",
        "NCCL_CROSS_NIC=1",
        "NCCL_COLLNET_ENABLE=1",
        "NCCL_NET=AWS Libfabric",
        "LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/soft/libraries/aws-ofi-nccl/v1.9.1-aws/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
        "LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/soft/libraries/hwloc/lib/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
        "FI_CXI_DISABLE_HOST_REGISTER=1",
        "FI_MR_CACHE_MONITOR=userfaultfd",
        "FI_CXI_DEFAULT_CQ_SIZE=131072",
        "NCCL_DEBUG=INFO"
      ]
    },
    "script_details": {
      "purpose": "Running various MPI configurations with NCCL for benchmarking",
      "configurations": [
        "single node with 4 ranks",
        "two nodes with 1 rank",
        "two nodes with 4 ranks",
        "two nodes with 8 ranks"
      ],
      "output_directory": "logs0_2"
    }
  }
}
```
